                                </td>
                            </tr>

                        [% END %]

                    </tbody>

                </table>
            </div>

        [% ELSE %]

            No items found. Please ask your system administrator to ensure that update-holds-to-pull.pl gets run regularily.

        [% END %]

    </div>

